Creating and Accessing a Cloud-hosted Linux Virtual Machine

With the Google Cloud Platform, setting up and accessing a Linux system only requires a few easy steps. This article will show you how to create a virtual machine on the Google Cloud Platform and access it using SSH, regardless of your level of cloud computing knowledge.

